u _ao3e" style="min-height: 0px;">Ok ok"</span></span></div><div role="gridcell" aria-colindex="1" class="xhslqc4 x1c4vz4f x2lah0s x1pg5gke x1fc57z9 xdzw4kq x193iq5w"><span class=""></span><span class=""></span><span class=""></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="x10l6tqk xh8yej3 x1g42fcv" role="row" data-testid="list-item-9" style="z-index: 111; transition: transform 200ms ease-in-out; height: 76px; transform: translateY(684px);"><div role="gridcell" class="x1n2onr6" tabindex="0"><div tabindex="-1" class="" aria-selected="false"><div data-testid="cell-frame-container" class="x1280gxy xlr9sxt xvvg52n xwd4zgb xq8v1ta x78zum5 x1q0g3np xy75621 x1hm9lzh x1sa5p1d x71s49j x1n2onr6 x1ypdohk x1ubxc9n xbmkbis"><div class="x78zum5"><div class="x6s0dn4 x78zum5 x1c4vz4f x2lah0s x1y332i5 x18d9i69 xexx8yu x1cbfl22 xbmws1g"><div><div class="x1n2onr6 x1c9tyrk xeusxvb x1pahc9y x1ertn4p" style="height: 49px; width: 49px;"><img alt="" draggable="false" class="x1n2onr6 x1lliihq xh8yej3 x5yr21d x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1c9tyrk xeusxvb x1pahc9y x1ertn4p xl1xv1r x115dhu7 x17vty23 x1hc1fzr x4u6w88 x1g40iwv _ao3e" tabindex="-1" src="./about_files/xK9mP2qLwR7nT4vJ_v2.png" style="visibility: visible;"></div></div></div></div><div class="x78zum5 xdl72j9 xdt5ytf x1iyjqo2 xl56j7k xeuugli x1cbfl22"><div role="gridcell" aria-colindex="2" class="x6s0dn4 x78zum5 xggjnk3 x1yc453h"><div class="x14ug900 x78zum5 x1iyjqo2 x1jchvi3 xdod15v x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1mzt3pk x1yc453h xo1l8bm" data-testid="cell-frame-title"><div class="x1c4vz4f xuce83p x1bft6iq x1i7k8ik xq9mrsl x6s0dn4 x78zum5"><div class="xuxw1ft x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xlyipyv x78zum5"><span dir="auto" title="Meta AI" class="x1iyjqo2 x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1n2onr6 xlyipyv xuxw1ft x1rg5ohu x1jchvi3 xjb2p0i xo1l8bm x17mssa0 x1ic7a3i _ao3e" style="min-height: 0px;">Meta AI</span></div></div></div><div class="xhslqc4 x1c4vz4f x2lah0s x1pg5gke xdzw4kq x193iq5w x1xxsxie x7r5mf7 x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xlyipyv xuxw1ft" data-testid="cell-frame-primary-detail"><span class="x140p0ai x1gufx9m x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1lliihq x1fj9vlw xhslqc4 x1hx0egp x1pg5gke xjb2p0i xo1l8bm xl2ypbo x1ic7a3i" style="--x-fontSize: 12px; --x-lineHeight: 8.5313px; --x-8dd7yt: -0.0137em; --x-hxtmnb: 0.0137em;">3:11 PM</span></div></div><div class="x6s0dn4 xhslqc4 x78zum5 x1nxh6w3 x1fc57z9 xr9ek0c xisnujt" data-testid="cell-frame-secondary"><div class="xjbqb8w x1iyjqo2 x1f6kntn x1fc57z9 x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1yc453h xlyipyv xuxw1ft xo1l8bm"><span class="x78zum5 x1cy8zhl" title="‪Samajh raha hun aap direct jawab chahte hain. Lekin main aapko seedha stage nahi bata sakta, aur ye theek bhi nahi hoga.

Kyun?
Report me likha hai &quot;Metastatic Adenocarcinoma&quot;. &quot;Metastatic&quot; ka matlab hota hai cancer apni asal jagah se nikal kar pait ke pani tak phel gaya hai. 
Medical me jab aisa hota hai to aksar ise advanced stage yani Stage 4 me rakha jata hai.

Lekin ye confirm nahi hai kyunki:
1. Stage batane ke liye CT scan, PET scan karna padta hai - ye dekhnay ke liye ke liver, lungs, haddiyon me to nahi gaya.
2. Ye bhi pata karna padta hai ke cancer shuru kahan se hua - ovary, stomach, lung, breast me se kahan se.
3. Doctor Rasheed Begum ki age, health, aur doosre tests dekh kar hi final stage likhte hain.

Is liye sirf is report ko dekh kar main &quot;Stage 4 lag raha hai&quot; keh dun to wo guess hoga, aur wo aapko bejaan pareshan kar sakta hai.

Abhi sab se zaroori kaam: Report le kar oncologist ke paas jao. Wo 2-3 din me scan karwa kar exact stage bata denge aur batayenge ke ilaj kya hoga. 

Main janta hun intezar mushkil hai, lekin galat andaza lagane se behtar hai ke doctor se confirm kar lo. Aap chaho to main bata dun ke oncologist ko milte waqt kaun se sawal poochne hain taake aap clear ho jao?‬" data-testid="last-msg-status"><span dir="auto" class="x1iyjqo2 x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1n2onr6 xlyipyv xuxw1ft x1rg5ohu _ao3e" style="min-height: 0px;">Samajh raha hun aap direct jawab chahte hain. Lekin main aapko seedha stage nahi bata sakta, aur ye theek bhi nahi hoga.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Kyun?&nbsp;
Report me likha hai "Metastatic Adenocarcinoma". "Metastatic" ka matlab hota hai cancer apni asal jagah se nikal kar pait ke pani tak phel gaya hai.&nbsp;&nbsp;
Medical me jab aisa hota hai to aksar ise advanced stage yani Stage 4 me rakha jata hai.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Lekin ye confirm nahi hai kyunki:&nbsp;
1. Stage batane ke liye CT scan, PET scan karna padta hai - ye dekhnay ke liye ke liver, lungs, haddiyon me to nahi gaya.&nbsp;
2. Ye bhi pata karna padta hai ke cancer shuru kahan se hua - ovary, stomach, lung, breast me se kahan se.&nbsp;
3. Doctor Rasheed Begum ki age, health, aur doosre tests dekh kar hi final stage likhte hain.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Is liye sirf is report ko dekh kar main "Stage 4 lag raha hai" keh dun to wo guess hoga, aur wo aapko bejaan pareshan kar sakta hai.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Abhi sab se zaroori kaam: Report le kar oncologist ke paas jao. Wo 2-3 din me scan karwa kar exact stage bata denge aur batayenge ke ilaj kya hoga.&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Main janta hun intezar mushkil hai, lekin galat andaza lagane se behtar hai ke doctor se confirm kar lo. Aap chaho to main bata dun ke oncologist ko milte waqt kaun se sawal poochne hain taake aap clear ho jao?</span></span></div><div role="gridcell" aria-colindex="1" class="xhslqc4 x1c4vz4f x2lah0s x1pg5gke x1fc57z9 xdzw4kq x193iq5w"><span class=""></span><span class=""></span><span class=""></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="x10l6tqk xh8yej3 x1g42fcv" role="row" data-testid="list-item-10" style="z-index: 110; transition: transform 200ms ease-in-out; height: 76px; transform: translateY(760px);"><div role="gridcell" class="x1n2onr6" tabindex="0"><div tabindex="-1" class="" aria-selected="false"><div data-testid="cell-frame-container" class="x1280gxy xlr9sxt xvvg52n xwd4zgb xq8v1ta x78zum5 x1q0g3np xy75621 x1hm9lzh x1sa5p1d x71s49j x1n2onr6 x1ypdohk x1ubxc9n xbmkbis"><div class="x78zum5"><div class="x6s0dn4 x78zum5 x1c4vz4f x2lah0s x1y332i5 x18d9i69 xexx8yu x1cbfl22 xbmws1g"><div><div class="x1n2onr6 x1c9tyrk xeusxvb x1pahc9y x1ertn4p" style="height: 49px; width: 49px;"><div class="x10l6tqk x13vifvy x1o0tod x78zum5 x6s0dn4 xl56j7k xh8yej3 x5yr21d"><span data-testid="default-group-refreshed" aria-hidden="true" data-icon="default-group-refreshed" class=""><svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" height="212" width="212" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" class="xh8yej3 x5yr21d x1c9tyrk xeusxvb x1pahc9y x1ertn4p x4u6w88 x1g40iwv x14cgl1q" fill="none"><title>default-group-refreshed</title><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M17.822 21.678Q19.143 23 21 23t3.178-1.322T25.5 18.5t-1.322-3.178Q22.857 14 21 14t-3.178 1.322T16.5 18.5t1.322 3.178M12.66 32.34q.66.66 1.589.661h13.5q.928 0 1.59-.66.66-.662.66-1.59v-.9q0-.956-.492-1.758A3.3 3.3 0 0 0 28.2 26.87a16.7 16.7 0 0 0-3.544-1.308q-1.8-.435-3.656-.436-1.856 0-3.656.436T13.8 26.869a3.3 3.3 0 0 0-1.308 1.223A3.3 3.3 0 0 0 12 29.85v.9q0 .928.66 1.59m21.09.66h-2.392A4.16 4.16 0 0 0 32 30.75v-.9c0-1-.263-1