May Allah bless all parents with good health, happiness and a long life <img crossorigin="anonymous" alt="🌸" draggable="false" class="b22 emoji wa  _ao3e" tabindex="-1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" style="background-position: 0px -60px;">
And for those whose loved ones are no longer in this world, may Allah grant them forgiveness, endless mercy and the highest place in Jannat ul firdous
May they be blessed with the shifaat of Hazrat Muhammad ﷺ and eternal peace<img crossorigin="anonymous" alt="🌸" draggable="false" class="b22 emoji wa  _ao3e" tabindex="-1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" style="background-position: 0px -60px;">

